    <title type="html"><![CDATA[git push 错误]]></title>
    <link href="http://jasonllinux.github.com/blog/2012/10/18/git-push-%E9%94%99%E8%AF%AF/"/>
    <updated>2012-10-18T00:00:00+08:00</updated>
    <id>http://jasonllinux.github.com/blog/2012/10/18/git-push-错误</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>今天，上传代码到github上的时候 莫名其妙出现：</p>

<p>[bash]<br />
Unable to rewind rpc post data - try increasing http.postBuffer<br />
error: RPC failed; result=65, HTTP code = 401<br />
fatal: The remote end hung up unexpectedly<br />
fatal: The remote end hung up unexpectedly<br />
[/bash]</p>

<p>解决方案：</p>

<p>[bash]<br />
git config http.postBuffer 209715200<br />
[/bash]</p>
]]></content>
